uding Ohmic resistivity\nonly. It will be important to examine how the Hall effect modifies the\nevolution, and to explore the influence this has on the observational\nappearance of such systems, and on planet formation and migration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 22 Jan 2015 09:09:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-23"}
